Ketua Kampung Sim, anda hebat!

00:27:14.112 --> 00:27:16.197
Gae!

00:27:17.240 --> 00:27:19.909
Hei, yut nori sangat menyeronokkan!

00:27:19.993 --> 00:27:22.495
-Puan Presiden, gae, satu, dua.
-Buat, gae.

00:27:22.579 --> 00:27:23.830
Betul.

00:27:23.913 --> 00:27:26.458
Bukankah ibu Dr. Song
ialah dewi yut nori?

